  "texts": [
    "Aspects such as experience design, its application in various domains such as museums or education, the utilization of technologies such as photogrammetry and the incorporation of VHs will all be analysed.",
    "The chronological structure of the analysis covers the steps involved in creating those sorts of iVR experience.",
    "An overview of the review structure, based on the review of Hovart et al. [28], is provided in Fig.",
    "According to that paper, the design of iVR experiences can be divided into 3 phases: preparation, execution, and post-processing.",
    "At each stage of the design of an iVR experience of CH reconstruction, the most relevant items identified in the review articles were analysed."
  ]
}